></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionstart_event\"><code>transitionstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcechanged_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcechanged</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcedown_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcedown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforceup_event\"><code>webkitmouseforceup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcewillbegin_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcewillbegin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/wheel_event\"><code>wheel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p><b>clientWidth</b> to wewnętrzna szerokość elementu w pikselach. Zawiera margines wewnętrzny (\n <i>\n  padding</i>\n ), ale pomija pionowy pasek przewijania (jeśli jest obecny lub renderowany), obramowania i margines zewnętrzny (\n <i>\n  margin</i>\n ).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia_i_warto.c5.9bci","title":"Składnia i wartości","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">var <var>w</var> = <var>element</var>.clientWidth;\n</pre>\n<p><var>w</var> to liczba całkowita odpowiadająca <b>clientWidth</b> <var>element</var>u w pikselach. <b>clientWidth</b> jest tylko do odczytu.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<div id=\"offsetcontainer\" style=\"margin: 26px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 204); border: 4px dashed black; color: black; position: absolute; left: 260px;\">\n <div id=\"iddiv\" style=\"margin: 24px 29px; border: 24px black solid; padding: 0px 28px; width: 199px; height: 102px; overflow: auto; background-color: white; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\n  <p id=\"PaddingTopLabel\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">padding-top</p>\n  <p>Gentle, individualistic and very loyal, Birman cats fall between Siamese and Persian in character. If you admire cats that are non aggressive, that enjoy being with humans and tend to be on the quiet side, you may well find that Birman cats are just the felines for you.</p>\n  <p><span style=\"float: right;\"><img alt=\"Image:BirmanCat.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></span>All Birmans have colorpointed features, dark coloration of the face, ears, legs and tail.</p>\n  <p>Cat image and text coming from <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://www.best-cat-art.com/\" rel=\" noopener\">www.best-cat-art.com</a></p>\n  <p id=\"PaddingBottomLabel\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">padding-bottom</p>\n </div>\n <span style=\"position: absolute; left: -32px; top: 85px; color: blue; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Left</span><span style=\"position: absolute; left: 170px; top: -24px; color: blue; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Top</span><span style=\"position: absolute; left: 370px; top: 85px; color: blue; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Right</span><span style=\"position: absolute; left: 164px; top: 203px; color: blue; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Bottom</span><span style=\"position: absolute; left: 143px; top: 5px; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">margin-top</span><span style=\"position: absolute; left: 138px; top: 175px; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">margin-bottom</span><span style=\"position: absolute; left: 143px; top: 27px; color: white; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">border-top</span><span style=\"position: absolute; left: 138px; top: 153px; color: white; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px!important; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">border-bottom</span><span class=\"comment\">[if IE]&gt;&lt;span id=\"MrgLeft\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 8px; top: 65px; font: bold 13px Arial, sans-serif&nbsp;!important; writing-mode: tb-rl;\"&gt;margin-left&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=\"BrdLeft\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 33px; top: 65px; color: white; font: bold 13px Arial, sans-serif&nbsp;!important; writing-mode: tb-rl;\"&gt;border-left&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=\"PdgLeft\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 55px; top: 65px; font: bold 13px Arial, sans-serif&nbsp;!important; writing-mode: tb-rl;\"&gt;padding-left&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=\"PdgRight\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 275px; top: 60px; color: black; font: bold 13px Arial, sans-serif&nbsp;!important; writing-mode: tb-rl; white-space: nowrap;\"&gt;padding-right&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=\"BrdRight\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 310px; top: 65px; color: white; font: bold 13px Arial, sans-serif&nbsp;!important; writing-mode: tb-rl;\"&gt;border-right&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=\"MrgRight\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 340px; top: 65px; font: bold 13px Arial, sans-serif&nbsp;!important; writing-mode: tb-rl;\"&gt;margin-right&lt;/span&gt;&lt;![endif]</span></div>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 270px;\"><img alt=\"Image:clientWidth.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Nie należy do żadnej ze specyfikacji W3C.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p><b>clientWidth</b> został wprowadzony w modelu obiektowym DHTML przeglądarki Internet Explorer.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dokumentacja","title":"Dokumentacja","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/workshop/author/dhtml/reference/properties/clientwidth.asp?frame=true\" rel=\" noopener\">MSDN clientWidth definition</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/workshop/author/om/measuring.asp\" rel=\" noopener\">MSDN Measuring Element Dimension and Location</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.mozilla.org/docs/dom/domref/clientWidth.html\" rel=\" noopener\">Gecko DOM Reference on clientWidth</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"clientWidth to wewnętrzna szerokość elementu w pikselach. Zawiera margines wewnętrzny (\n \n  padding\n ), ale pomija pionowy pasek przewijania (jeśli jest obecny lub renderowany), obramowania i margines zewnętrzny (\n \n  margin\n ).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element.clientWidth","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element.clientWidth","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.clientWidth","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Element.clientWidth","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Element.clientWidth","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Element.clientWidth","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Element.clientWidth","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/element/clientwidth","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/element/clientwidth/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/clientWidth","title":"element.clientWidth"}],"pageTitle":"element.clientWidth - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}